query:
INSERT INTO map (
                gbx_mapuid, gbx_data, mapname, ap_author_id, created,
                thumbnail, thumbnail_small,
                author_medal_ms, gold_medal_ms, silver_medal_ms, bronze_medal_ms 
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, to_timestamp($5),
                $6, $7,
                $8, $9, $10, $11
            )
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
            RETURNING ap_map_id
